    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_035_000002",
    "sentence": "張純字伯仁，京兆杜陵人也。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_035_000003",
    "sentence": "高祖父安世，宣帝時為大司馬衛將軍，封富平侯。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "司馬",
        "label": "TITLE",
